03 Feb 2009 17:20






You're probably thinking about Gleep and Gloop from "The Herculoids". They were one of my inspirations for writing this, along with my own two cats and my childhood love of Silly Putty. The idea behind this was that I was trying to make something that was 682's complete opposite: a cuddly, tickley blob of pure happiness that loves all creatures great and small.

As for the smiling- I figured if 682 is so adaptive, it would develop the ability to smile and laugh in the presence of 1011- as well as gain its tickling powers.







